        <Parent_String>thermoplastic [300014415], plastic by property [300167623], plastic (material) [300014570], organic material [300011792], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
